reviews.text: Great place to shop for good quality seafood. Not the cheap kid thou

A small market with different kind of fresh seafoods, local catch or imported, which you can choose and bring it to restuarants opposite the street for cooking.  You can request for different styles of cooking.  If you are not familiar with the best way of cooking, I suggest you ask for professional help in the restaurants.
I had help with my friend's family ordering all the seafood that we got to hand pick, but everything was delicious. It was an amazing experience to have with friends and family. Thank you!
Seafood market and seafood restaurants
